data.description: Welcome to one of Murrieta's most competitively priced townhomes! Boasting 1,590 sq. ft. of stylish living space, this 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom gem offers an open-concept layout that's perfect for both entertaining and everyday life. Delight in the modern touches of the upgraded kitchen, where culinary dreams come alive. The main floor also houses a convenient half bath for guests. Moving upstairs to find three generously-sized bedrooms. Each guest room radiates warmth and space, sharing access to a pristine guest bathroom. The expansive master suite, complete with a spacious master bath and ample closet storage. Imagine retreating to this sanctuary after a long day! Situated in the heart of Murrieta, this townhome is is not just comfortable & ideal for families but it is also of incredible value.
